        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/golden/mission_gecko/scene_gecko_basic.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 5711a570-eefa-44ac-a8a3-d72ef2880f1e).Image",
        "Description": "Ditlon is by far the world&apos;s most successful vacuum cleaner manufacturer; so much so that they have put most of their competitors out of business.\r\rThis is partly due to the vacuum&apos;s efficiency and robust design, but mostly due to Ditlon&apos;s frequent violation of competition law.\r\rTheir competitors are powerless to stop them, and so have instead hired us to destroy Ditlon&apos;s reputation.\r\rThey believe that a series of explosions resulting from &quot;faulty Ditlon vacuum cleaners&quot; should do the trick.",
